### EduPortal API - Sports Assessments Controller
### Sports assessment management endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:5000
### Requires Authentication

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/sports-assessments
@contentType = application/json
@token = {{$dotenv TOKEN}}

### ===========================================
### GET ALL SPORTS ASSESSMENTS
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET SPORTS ASSESSMENT SUMMARIES
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/summaries
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET SPORTS ASSESSMENT BY ID
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET SPORTS ASSESSMENTS BY STUDENT
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/student/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET SPORTS ASSESSMENTS BY COACH
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/coach/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET SPORTS ASSESSMENT STATISTICS
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### CREATE SPORTS ASSESSMENT - (Admin, Coach, Danışman)
### ===========================================
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "studentId": 1,
  "coachId": 1,
  "assessmentDate": "2024-11-15",
  "sportType": "Basketball",
  "skillLevel": "Intermediate",
  "athleticAbilities": ["Speed", "Agility", "Teamwork"],
  "achievements": ["Okul takımı kaptanı"],
  "recruitmentPotential": "D3",
  "notes": "Spor değerlendirmesi"
}

### ===========================================
### UPDATE SPORTS ASSESSMENT - (Admin, Coach, Danışman)
### ===========================================
PUT {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "skillLevel": "Advanced",
  "recruitmentPotential": "D2",
  "notes": "Gelişme kaydedildi"
}

### ===========================================
### DELETE SPORTS ASSESSMENT - (Admin only)
### ===========================================
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

